{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/debugcontrollerdbusprotocol\/onnotifyconnection(flags:handler:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyConnection","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"DebugControllerDBusRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO22DebugControllerDBusRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBusRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"C","type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This represents the underlying ","type":"text"},{"code":"notify::connection","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBusProtocol\/onNotifyConnection(flags:handler:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DebugControllerDBusProtocol"]]},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO27DebugControllerDBusProtocolPAAE18onNotifyConnection5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bcD3RefV_AG09ParamSpecO0VtctF","extendedModule":"GIO","title":"onNotifyConnection(flags:handler:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyConnection","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"text":"DebugControllerDBusRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO22DebugControllerDBusRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}]},"section